Mrs. Devereaux. We weren't
expecting you until tomorrow.

59
00:03:09,489 --> 00:03:14,119
A lady should never do
what anyone expects of her, Henry.

60
00:03:14,227 --> 00:03:17,492
<i>[George Narrating] My parents'</i>
<i>marriage is not what you'd call seamless.</i>

61
00:03:17,597 --> 00:03:20,327
[Elevator Bell Dings]

62
00:03:20,433 --> 00:03:22,401
Holy shit.

63
00:03:22,502 --> 00:03:24,663
Yep.

64
00:03:24,771 --> 00:03:27,001
<i>[Narrating]</i>
<i>My father's a band leader.</i>

65
00:03:27,106 --> 00:03:29,836
