<i>off a song he wrote called...</i>

70
00:03:41,521 --> 00:03:44,319
# My one and only #

71
00:03:44,424 --> 00:03:47,587
<i>The only thing louder</i>
<i>than its arrangement is its irony.</i>

72
00:03:47,694 --> 00:03:50,094
<i>My father is an artist...</i>

73
00:03:50,196 --> 00:03:53,063
<i>with all the strengths</i>
<i>and weaknesses that implies.</i>

74
00:03:53,166 --> 00:03:55,634
- <i>[Knocking On Door]</i>
- <i>[Man] Dan, two-minute call.</i>

75
00:03:55,735 --> 00:03:58,363
- Comin'.
- <i>As much as my father's life...</i>

76
00:03:58,471 --> 00:04:00,405
relies upon improvisation...

77
